About Us





About Us
Genius Brands is a multi-media entertainment company dedicated to providing "content with a purpose" for toddlers to tweens. This means content that is as enriching as it is entertaining.
We've tapped into the wisdom of Warren Buffett, the creative genius of Stan Lee, and other brilliant minds to create a portfolio of entertainment that engages, entertains, and enriches young minds.
Genius Brands is led by a team of highly accomplished and experienced professionals in children’s entertainment.
Andy (Chairman & CEO) is a multi-Emmy winning producer of children's entertainment. Andy is the former Chairman & CEO of DIC Entertainment, where he produced more than 5,000 episodes of children's entertainment, including Inspector Gadget, Ghostbusters, Strawberry Shortcake, Alvin & the Chipmunks, Super Mario Brothers, Hello Kitty, Sonic the Hedgehog, Captain Planet, G.I. Joe, Madeline, Sabrina the Teenage Witch, the Archies, and dozens more. He is an award-winning producer with multiple Emmys, CableAce, Humanitas and Environmental Media awards to his credit, as well as being appointed to the Kidscreen Hall of Fame and named an honoree at the prestigious International Cartoons on the Bay.
Amy (President) has spent the past 20 years creating, launching and managing some of the most valuable brands in the world. She was part of the original team who created and launched Disney Cruise Line. She has also worked for Universal Studios and Hasbro in different capacities on dozens of new brands for kids. And as Director of Global Marketing at McDonald's, she worked with kids entertainment brands from all around the world. The management team is comprised of accomplished and passionate professionals including Emmy award-winning Directors and Producers, Sales, Marketing, and Business Development executives.
Contact us for more information.
Genius Brands is dedicated to entertaining and enriching "content with a purpose." 








 


