Llama Llama





The award-winning Llama Llama series, known for its emotive content, signature characters, family relationships, and addressing the everyday issues of young children, includes Llama Llama Red Pajama, Llama Lama and the Bully Goat, Llama Lama Time to Share, Llama Llama Misses Mama, Llama Llama Holiday Drama, and Llama Llama Mad at Mama.
With 9.4 million units in print, Anna Dewdney’s Llama Llama books have all been New York Times bestsellers with several titles claiming the #1 spot.


Llama LlamaA little llama who loves his mama!Llama Llama likes to play all kinds of games with his friends and he carries his stuffed animal, Fuzzy llama, everywhere he goes. Sometimes, he worries about new things.
 



Mama LlamaMama Llama is a busy, working mom.Mama Llama loves her little lllama. At times she can get exasperated by him and all the things she needs to do, but she always has fun with her little llama.
 



Nelly GnuNelly Gnu is Llama Llama's best friend. Nelly Gnu is spunky, asks lots of questions, and sometimes gets into trouble. Nelly likes to build and paint things. Her favorite colors are purple and blue.
 



GilroyGilroy is Llama Llama's classmate.Gilroy can sometimes do and say things that are not nice and that hurt other people's feelings. Gilroy is not mean, but he has a hard time controlling what he does and says.
 



Fuzzy LlamaLlama Llama's special stuffed animal.Fuzzy Llama follows Llama Llama wherever he goes. You can always tell what Fuzzy Llama is thinking by the expression on his face.
 

http://www.llamallamabook.com/ 













 


