			Company Description 


			Genius Brands International, Inc. is a multimedia content and brand management company. It provides entertaining and enriching content and products; and creates and licenses multimedia content for toddlers to tweens. It also produces an animated preschool series based on Llama Llama and a tween adve...
		


                Genius Brands International, Inc. is a multimedia content and brand management company. It provides entertaining and enriching content and products; and creates and licenses multimedia content for toddlers to tweens. It also produces an animated preschool series based on Llama Llama and a tween adventure series, Space Pop. Genius Brands International acts as a licensing agent for certain brands, such as Llama Llama, Psycho Bunny, From Frank and Celessence Technologies. The company was founded by Balaban Howard Alan on January 2, 2006 and is headquartered in Beverly Hills, CA.
            




